description:
Implement parseAzdoRemote(url: string): AzdoContext | null that extracts org and project from Azure DevOps git remote URLs. Must support all 5 cloud URL formats per research.md:

1. HTTPS current: https://dev.azure.com/{org}/{project}/_git/{repo}
2. HTTPS legacy: https://{org}.visualstudio.com/{project}/_git/{repo}
3. HTTPS legacy+DC: https://{org}.visualstudio.com/DefaultCollection/{project}/_git/{repo}
4. SSH current: git@ssh.dev.azure.com:v3/{org}/{project}/{repo}
5. SSH legacy: {org}@vs-ssh.visualstudio.com:v3/{org}/{project}/{repo}

Returns AzdoContext (org + project) on match, null for non-Azure URLs (GitHub, GitLab, etc.).
